criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Healthy adults suffering from upper and lower denture indicated for replacement due to
             use exceeding five years;

          2. Have availability to attend FO / UFPel days predetermined;

          3. Agree with the term informed consent, approved by the research ethics committee of FO
             / UFPel.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients younger than 40 years;

          2. Patients who are not users of denture upper and lower;

          3. Patients denture wearers during periods of less than five years.
